{"_id":"01e56g5ii5g65e10","name":"Voice of the Spirits","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","scenarioSlug":"red-hood-iskra","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"128","contentKey":"scenario-gift.red-hood-iskra.voice-of-the-spirits","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":1,"folderName":"Red-Hood Iskra","specialFor":"","translations":{"es":{"name":"Voz de los espíritus","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> haber estado en contacto con el don Espíritu.</p><p>Al calmar la mente y concentrarte, puedes abrirla al mundo espiritual y comunicarte con almas sin descanso. Gasta 1 Soma para contactar con una criatura que tenga el don Espíritu y a la que hayas encontrado previamente. No sufres la Herida causada por el estrés de la conexión espiritual.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - Red-Hood Iskra","requirements":"haber estado en contacto con el don Espíritu.","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra"},"scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"132"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> You have come into contact with the Gift Spirit.</p><p>By calming your mind and concentrating, you can open your mind to the spiritual world and communicate with restless souls. Spend 1 Soma to contact a creature with the Spirit Gift you’ve previously encountered. You do not suffer the Wound caused by the stress of spiritual connection.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - Red-Hood Iskra","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Red-Hood Iskra","source":"Red-Hood Iskra","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.red-hood-iskra.voice-of-the-spirits","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","scenarioSlug":"red-hood-iskra","sourceDirectory":"red-hood-iskra","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"You have come into contact with the Gift Spirit.","limitations":""},"sort":100000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086874,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"00sthrgxxgrhts00","name":"Wolf-killer","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","scenarioSlug":"red-hood-iskra","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"128","contentKey":"scenario-gift.red-hood-iskra.wolf-killer","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":2,"folderName":"Red-Hood Iskra","specialFor":"","translations":{"es":{"name":"Matalobos","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> haberse enfrentado con los lobos en un combate al menos una vez.</p><p>Sabes cómo enfrentarte a los lobos más feroces e intentas evitar que te rodeen. Cuando obtienes al menos un triunfo estándar en una prueba de posición o defensa contra una manada de bestias, puedes eliminar inmediatamente a 1 animal PNJ menor con 1 Herida.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - Red-Hood Iskra","requirements":"haberse enfrentado con los lobos en un combate al menos una vez.","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra"},"scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"132"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> Having faced the wolves in a fight at least once.</p><p>You know how to deal with the fiercest of wolves and are careful not to be surrounded. When you obtain at least a Standard Outcome on a Position or Defense Check against a pack of beasts, you can immediately eliminate 1 Minor animal NPC with 1 Wound.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - Red-Hood Iskra","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Red-Hood Iskra","source":"Red-Hood Iskra","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.red-hood-iskra.wolf-killer","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","scenarioSlug":"red-hood-iskra","sourceDirectory":"red-hood-iskra","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"Having faced the wolves in a fight at least once.","limitations":""},"sort":200000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086874,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"01j436i77i634j10","name":"Where are you going all alone, sweetie? (Special Gift for Garou the Old Wolf)","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","scenarioSlug":"red-hood-iskra","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"128","contentKey":"scenario-gift.red-hood-iskra.where-are-you-going-all-alone-sweetie","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":3,"folderName":"Red-Hood Iskra","specialFor":"Garou the Old Wolf","translations":{"es":{"name":"Caperucita: ¿dónde vas tú tan solita? (don especial para Garou, el Viejo Lobo)","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> encontrar a Iskra sola en el bosque.</p><p>Te sientes atraído por la niña que finge ser un lobo y sueñas con devorarla. Una vez por escena, puedes gastar 1 Soma para saber exactamente dónde está. Si te anticipas y llegas a algún lugar antes que ella, obtienes 1 Éxito adicional en todas las pruebas que realices para herir o devorar a ese pequeño bocado. No puedes esperar a devorarla y eso te hace bajar la guardia. Mientras ella esté presente en la escena, sufres 1 Penalizador en todas las pruebas de defensa.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - Red-Hood Iskra","requirements":"encontrar a Iskra sola en el bosque.","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra"},"scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"132"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> To meet Iskra alone in the forest.</p><p>You are attracted to the little girl who pretends to be a wolf and you dream of devouring her. Once per Scene, you can spend 1 Soma to know exactly where she is. If you anticipate her and arrive somewhere before her, you get 1 Additional Success on every Check you make to hurt or devour that little morsel. You can’t wait to swallow that tidbit and it makes you let your guard down. As long as she is present in the Scene, you receive 1 Penalty in all Defense Checks.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - Red-Hood Iskra","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Red-Hood Iskra","source":"Red-Hood Iskra","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.red-hood-iskra.where-are-you-going-all-alone-sweetie","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","scenarioSlug":"red-hood-iskra","sourceDirectory":"red-hood-iskra","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"To meet Iskra alone in the forest.","limitations":""},"sort":300000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086874,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
